bio.Bios: Hello! My name is Aryan, and I initiated the spring quarter of my freshman year with the Alpha Nu class! In my free time, you will find me exploring nature, staying active at the gym, and playing soccer. A fun fact about me is that I stuck my finger in a blender when I was a kid. Ask me about Formula 1 or my passion for cars at recruitment, I look forward to meeting you!
